data.title: 13446 S. Blackbob Rd, Olathe, KS
data.meta_description: Our Olathe Branch is located on W 134th Pl. and S. Black Blob Road on the north east side of Olathe, KS.
data.text:
Whether you need to open a new checking account or apply for a personal loan, Central Bank in Olathe, KS, is here to provide you with convenient banking solutions near you. Situated on the corner of South Blackbob Road and West 134th Place, our expert staff is ready to assist you with any of your personal banking, business banking, or home loan needs. You can find our branch right next door to Chuck E. Cheese, Walgreens, and St. Luke’s Community Hospital of Olathe.

As a member of the Olathe community, Central Bank is dedicated to providing residents and businesses with banking services they can count on. From notary services and cash management to safe deposit box access and more, we are here to help you manage your money with ease. Our convenient location is available with lobby and drive-through hours from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. Monday through Friday, and Saturday from 9 a.m. to noon.
